   To see what, for example, the first solution looks like and how it
relates to the constraints matrix Q8:

           вҚқ the rows in Q8 of the first solution
           вҚқ
           Z[1]
      1 14 24 27 39 44 50 61

           вҚқ the first solution translated back into the problem domain
           вҚқ
           {вҺ•UCS (65+вҢҠвҚөГ·8)(49+8вҲЈвҚөвҶҗвҚө-вҺ•IO)} ВЁ вҠғZ[1]
      A1 B6 C8 D3 E7 F4 G2 H5

           вҚқ the constraints of the rows of the first solution
           вҚқ
           Q8[вҠғZ[1];]
