2.35.7 Rotation
---------------

The rotation operation, вҺ•MX[7], is monadic and takes a real or complex
scalar angle and returns a 2-space rotation matrix:

           вҺ•MX[7] в—Ӣ30Г·180
     0.866 ВҜ0.5
     0.5    0.866


