2.37 вҺ•PNG - Portable Network Graphics
=====================================

Portable Network Graphics is a file format for images, defined in *RFC
2083*.  To quote the RFC:

   вҖҳThe PNG format provides a portable, legally unencumbered,
well-compressed, well-specified standard for lossless bitmapped image
files.вҖҷ

