5 Vector Notation
*****************

This chapter describes details of the GNU APL vector notation.
Unfortunately there exists misleading information concerning the GNU APL
vector notation on the public internet and the attempts of the author of
this manual to have the misleading information corrected were not
successful.

* Menu:

* History::
* Standardization::
* Quotes from the lrm::
* Some APL2 Tests::
